D
(DA)_{ii} = D_{ii} A_{ii}
tr(DA) = \sum_{i=1}^n D_{ii} A_{ii}
|tr(DA)| \leq \left ( \sum_{i=1}^n D_{ii}^2 \right )^{1/2} \left ( \sum_{i=1}^n A_{ii}^2 \right )^{1/2}
\| x \|_2 \leq \| x \|_1
|tr(DA)| \leq tr(|D|) tr(|A|)
(|D|)_{ij} = |D_{ij}|
|A|
